        </div>
        <a class="homebtn" href="@Url.Action("Index")"><i class='bx bx-left-arrow-alt' style="color:white"></i></a>
        <div class="sign-up-intro" id="sign-up-intro">

            <span>Morbi mollis eros ut rhoncus euismod. Duis ut lacus dictum, consequat elit sit amet, aliquam purus. Nulla id nisi tincidunt, viverra sem nec, hendrerit nisl. Ut a scelerisque risus. Etiam interdum congue commodo.</span>
            <button class="btn-signup" onclick="sig();">Sign Up</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

